    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-12-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-12-10T13:00:00-05:00" n="565"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d565">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.516/15.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">National Bank of the Republic of
                            Haiti</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1914-12-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1914-12-10T13:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>
                        <hi rend="italic">; received December 11, 1914.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Will you kindly have the following telegram transmitted to Port au Prince for our
                    account: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p rend="flushleft">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ban que Nation ale de la Republiqtte d’Haiti</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>.</p>
                        <p>Referring to our previous message, you are authorized to deliver gold to
                            Captain United States Ship <hi rend="italic">Machias</hi> due Port au
                            Prince fifteenth. Wire immediately amount you are shipping.</p>
                        <p rend="right">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wehrhane</hi>.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">National Bank of the Republic of Haiti</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
